<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Photo Album Gift Page</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Special+Elite&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000, #312e3e, #423c2e, #1e262f, #1a2b27);
            background-size: 200% 200%;
            animation: glowGradient 12s ease infinite;
            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        @keyframes glowGradient {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        .album-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #181a18be, #171817);
            border: 10px solid #dfd69857;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            align-self: center;
        }

        .album-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            z-index: 0;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffcc5c;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .photo-grid {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: clamp(250px, 40vw, 400px);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .photo {
            position: absolute;
            width: clamp(120px, 15vw, 200px);
            height: clamp(150px, 20vw, 250px);
            background: #fff;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .photo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .photo img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        /* Animation keyframes for sliding effect */
        @keyframes slideIn {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%) scale(0.8); opacity: 0; }
            20% { transform: translateX(0) scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            80% { transform: translateX(0) scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%) scale(0.8); opacity: 0; }
        }

        .photo-1 { left: 5%; top: 10%; animation: slideIn 10s infinite; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .photo-2 { left: 25%; top: 30%; animation: slideIn 10s infinite; animation-delay: 2s; }
        .photo-3 { left: 45%; top: 5%; animation: slideIn 10s infinite; animation-delay: 4s; }
        .photo-4 { left: 65%; top: 25%; animation: slideIn 10s infinite; animation-delay: 6s; }
        .photo-5 { left: 85%; top: 45%; animation: slideIn 10s infinite; animation-delay: 8s; }

        .text-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d3dbad, #ccd1b8, #d0dab9);
            padding: 2rem;
            /* font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
             */
             font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', cursive;
             font-style:italic;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            min-height: 150px;
            box-shadow: 
                0 10px 25px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.3),
                inset 0 0 20px rgba(101, 67, 33, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: clamp(0.875rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            color: #4a3728d0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            clip-path: polygon(
                5% 0%, 
                85% 3%, 
                95% 8%, 
                100% 15%, 
                97% 25%, 
                100% 40%, 
                95% 55%, 
                98% 70%, 
                92% 85%, 
                85% 95%, 
                70% 98%, 
                50% 100%, 
                25% 97%, 
                15% 92%, 
                8% 85%, 
                3% 70%, 
                0% 50%, 
                2% 35%, 
                0% 20%, 
                3% 10%
            );
            transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
            border: none;
        }

        .text-box::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -10px;
            left: -10px;
            right: -10px;
            bottom: -10px;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.15) 0%, transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(101, 67, 33, 0.12) 0%, transparent 45%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 40% 80%, rgba(160, 82, 45, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 70% 20%, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.08) 0%, transparent 35%);
            clip-path: polygon(
                3% 0%, 
                87% 2%, 
                97% 6%, 
                100% 18%, 
                98% 28%, 
                100% 42%, 
                96% 58%, 
                99% 72%, 
                94% 87%, 
                87% 97%, 
                72% 99%, 
                48% 100%, 
                23% 98%, 
                13% 94%, 
                6% 87%, 
                1% 72%, 
                0% 48%, 
                1% 33%, 
                0% 18%, 
                1% 8%
            );
            z-index: -2;
            filter: blur(3px);
        }

        .text-box::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(
                    45deg,
                    transparent,
                    transparent 8px,
                    rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.02) 8px,
                    rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.02) 16px
                ),
                radial-gradient(circle at 15% 25%, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.08) 0%, transparent 25%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 85% 15%, rgba(101, 67, 33, 0.06) 0%, transparent 20%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 25% 85%, rgba(160, 82, 45, 0.05) 0%, transparent 15%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 75% 75%, rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.09) 0%, transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 60% 40%, rgba(101, 67, 33, 0.04) 0%, transparent 18%);
            clip-path: polygon(
                5% 0%, 
                85% 3%, 
                95% 8%, 
                100% 15%, 
                97% 25%, 
                100% 40%, 
                95% 55%, 
                98% 70%, 
                92% 85%, 
                85% 95%, 
                70% 98%, 
                50% 100%, 
                25% 97%, 
                15% 92%, 
                8% 85%, 
                3% 70%, 
                0% 50%, 
                2% 35%, 
                0% 20%, 
                3% 10%
            );
            z-index: -1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Additional torn pieces scattered around */
        .text-box .torn-piece {
            position: absolute;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #191919,#1a1b1a);
            z-index: 2;
            opacity: 0.89;
        }

        .text-box .torn-piece-1 {
            width: 20px;
            height: 35px;
            top: -15px;
            left: 20%;
            clip-path: polygon(20% 0%, 80% 5%, 100% 25%, 85% 60%, 90% 100%, 40% 95%, 0% 80%, 15% 40%);
            transform: rotate(25deg);
        }

        .text-box .torn-piece-2 {
            width: 25px;
            height: 20px;
            bottom: -10px;
            right: 30%;
            clip-path: polygon(0% 20%, 60% 0%, 100% 30%, 80% 70%, 100% 100%, 20% 80%, 0% 100%);
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }

        .text-box .torn-piece-3 {
            width: 30px;
            height: 15px;
            top: 30%;
            right: -12px;
            clip-path: polygon(0% 0%, 70% 10%, 100% 40%, 90% 80%, 60% 100%, 20% 90%, 0% 60%);
            transform: rotate(60deg);
        }

        .text-box .torn-piece-4 {
            width: 15px;
            height: 25px;
            bottom: 40%;
            left: -8px;
            clip-path: polygon(30% 0%, 100% 20%, 80% 50%, 100% 90%, 50% 100%, 0% 70%, 20% 30%);
            transform: rotate(-30deg);
        }

        .text-box:hover {
            box-shadow: 
                0 15px 35px rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.4),
                inset 0 0 25px rgba(101, 67, 33, 0.15);
            transform: rotate(-1deg) scale(1.02);
        }

        .popup {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            z-index: 1000;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .popup img {
            max-width: 95%;
            max-height: 95%;
            border: 8px solid #e4e5c741;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        .popup-close {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            color: #ffcc5c;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 1001;
        }

        .popup-close:hover {
            color: #50e3c2;
        }

        /* Tablet styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 0.5rem;
            }

            .album-container {
                padding: 1.5rem;
                border-width: 6px;
                margin: 1rem auto;
            }

            .photo-grid {
                height: clamp(200px, 35vw, 300px);
            }

            .photo {
                width: clamp(100px, 18vw, 150px);
                height: clamp(125px, 22vw, 190px);
            }

            .photo:hover {
                transform: scale(1.02);
            }

            .text-box {
                padding: 1rem;
                min-height: 120px;
                clip-path: polygon(
                    8% 0%, 
                    82% 4%, 
                    92% 10%, 
                    100% 18%, 
                    95% 28%, 
                    100% 45%, 
                    92% 60%, 
                    96% 75%, 
                    88% 88%, 
                    80% 96%, 
                    65% 98%, 
                    45% 100%, 
                    20% 95%, 
                    10% 88%, 
                    5% 80%, 
                    0% 65%, 
                    3% 45%, 
                    0% 25%, 
                    5% 12%
                );
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-1 {
                width: 15px;
                height: 25px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-2 {
                width: 20px;
                height: 15px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-3 {
                width: 22px;
                height: 12px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-4 {
                width: 12px;
                height: 20px;
            }
        }

        /* Mobile styles */
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            body {
                padding: 0.25rem;
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding-top: 1rem;
            }

            .album-container {
                padding: 1rem;
                border-width: 4px;
                margin: 0.5rem auto;
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .photo-grid {
                height: clamp(180px, 30vw, 250px);
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }

            .photo {
                width: clamp(80px, 20vw, 120px);
                height: clamp(100px, 25vw, 150px);
            }

            .photo-1 { left: 2%; top: 15%; }
            .photo-2 { left: 20%; top: 35%; }
            .photo-3 { left: 40%; top: 10%; }
            .photo-4 { left: 60%; top: 30%; }
            .photo-5 { left: 78%; top: 50%; }

            .text-box {
                padding: 0.75rem;
                min-height: 100px;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                clip-path: polygon(
                    10% 0%, 
                    80% 5%, 
                    90% 12%, 
                    100% 22%, 
                    93% 32%, 
                    100% 48%, 
                    90% 65%, 
                    94% 78%, 
                    85% 90%, 
                    75% 95%, 
                    60% 98%, 
                    40% 100%, 
                    18% 93%, 
                    8% 85%, 
                    3% 75%, 
                    0% 60%, 
                    5% 42%, 
                    0% 28%, 
                    7% 15%
                );
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-1 {
                width: 12px;
                height: 20px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-2 {
                width: 15px;
                height: 12px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-3 {
                width: 18px;
                height: 10px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-4 {
                width: 10px;
                height: 15px;
            }

            .popup-close {
                top: 10px;
                right: 10px;
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .popup img {
                border-width: 4px;
            }
        }

        /* Very small mobile devices */
        @media (max-width: 360px) {
            .album-container {
                padding: 0.75rem;
                border-width: 3px;
            }

            .photo-grid {
                height: clamp(150px, 25vw, 200px);
            }

            .photo {
                width: clamp(60px, 22vw, 100px);
                height: clamp(75px, 28vw, 125px);
            }

            .text-box {
                padding: 0.5rem;
                min-height: 80px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                clip-path: polygon(
                    12% 0%, 
                    78% 6%, 
                    88% 15%, 
                    100% 25%, 
                    90% 35%, 
                    100% 50%, 
                    88% 68%, 
                    92% 82%, 
                    82% 92%, 
                    70% 96%, 
                    55% 98%, 
                    35% 100%, 
                    15% 90%, 
                    6% 82%, 
                    0% 70%, 
                    2% 55%, 
                    0% 35%, 
                    8% 20%
                );
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-1 {
                width: 10px;
                height: 15px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-2 {
                width: 12px;
                height: 10px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-3 {
                width: 15px;
                height: 8px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-4 {
                width: 8px;
                height: 12px;
            }
        }

        /* Landscape orientation on mobile */
        @media (max-width: 896px) and (orientation: landscape) {
            body {
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding-top: 0.5rem;
            }

            .album-container {
                margin: 0.5rem auto;
            }

            .photo-grid {
                height: clamp(120px, 20vw, 200px);
            }

            .photo {
                width: clamp(80px, 12vw, 120px);
                height: clamp(100px, 15vw, 150px);
            }

            h1 {
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

            .text-box {
                min-height: 80px;
                clip-path: polygon(
                    15% 0%, 
                    75% 8%, 
                    85% 18%, 
                    100% 30%, 
                    88% 40%, 
                    100% 55%, 
                    85% 72%, 
                    90% 85%, 
                    80% 95%, 
                    65% 98%, 
                    50% 100%, 
                    30% 97%, 
                    12% 88%, 
                    3% 80%, 
                    0% 65%, 
                    5% 50%, 
                    0% 30%, 
                    10% 15%
                );
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-1 {
                width: 8px;
                height: 12px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-2 {
                width: 10px;
                height: 8px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-3 {
                width: 12px;
                height: 6px;
            }

            .text-box .torn-piece-4 {
                width: 6px;
                height: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="album-container">
        <div class="photo-grid">
            <div class="photo photo-1"><img src="/asset/19page.jpg" alt="Memory 1"></div>
            <div class="photo photo-2"><img src="/asset/19page1.jpg" alt="Memory 2"></div>
            <div class="photo photo-3"><img src="/asset/19page2.jpg" alt="Memory 3"></div>
            <div class="photo photo-4"><img src="/asset/19page3.jpg" alt="Memory 4"></div>
            <div class="photo photo-5"><img src="/asset/19page4.jpg" alt="Memory 5"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-box">
            <div class="torn-piece torn-piece-1"></div>
            <div class="torn-piece torn-piece-2"></div>
            <div class="torn-piece torn-piece-3"></div>
            <div class="torn-piece torn-piece-4"></div>
            "A paper camera..some paper photos..but my feelings for you is real and you are as colorfull as you in my heart..Every photo of you makes me smile girl...I cherrish you always"
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="popup" id="imagePopup">
        <span class="popup-close"></span>
        <img src="" alt="Popup Image">
    </div>

    <script>
        const photos = document.querySelectorAll('.photo img');
        const popup = document.getElementById('imagePopup');
        const popupImg = popup.querySelector('img');
        const closeBtn = popup.querySelector('.popup-close');

        photos.forEach(img => {
            img.addEventListener('click', () => {
                popupImg.src = img.src;
                popup.style.display = 'flex';
            });
        });

        closeBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            popup.style.display = 'none';
        });

        popup.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            if (e.target === popup) {
                popup.style.display = 'none';
            }
        });

        // Prevent zoom on double-tap for iOS
        let lastTouchEnd = 0;
        document.addEventListener('touchend', function (event) {
            const now = (new Date()).getTime();
            if (now - lastTouchEnd <= 300) {
                event.preventDefault();
            }
            lastTouchEnd = now;
        }, false);
    </script>
</body>

</html>